msgctxt ""
"04120211.xhp\n"
"par_id1209200804373840\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also assign the outline levels in the <link href=\"text/swriter/01/05030800.xhp\">Outline & Numbering</link> tab page of the Format - Paragraph dialog."
